<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><rss version="2.0"><channel><title>Romio Joseph | Blog</title><description>In pursuit of happiness. I like working at startups, helping out with open-source projects, and exploring the future of digital creation using natural language.</description><link>https://romiojoseph.github.io/</link><language>en-us</language><item><title>AT Proto tools and Bluesky clients</title><link>https://romiojoseph.github.io/blog/post/at-proto-tools-and-bluesky-clients/</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://romiojoseph.github.io/blog/post/at-proto-tools-and-bluesky-clients/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://cdn.bsky.app/img/feed_thumbnail/plain/did:plc:xglrcj6gmrpktysohindaqhj/bafkreicei3qwscbhq5o3tvsmu3wfbqxi7rzks4mshlgcty4wodtgmhkyse@jpeg&quot; alt=&quot;AT Proto tools and Bluesky clients&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Repository browsing, Bluesky analytics, content exports, video downloads, advanced search, screenshot tools and more.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://romiojoseph.github.io/blog/post/at-proto-tools-and-bluesky-clients/&quot;&gt;Read more on the blog...&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Sat, 28 Feb 2026 23:30:00 GMT</pubDate></item><item><title>The Hidden Costs Of Convenience</title><link>https://romiojoseph.github.io/blog/post/the-hidden-costs-of-convenience/</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://romiojoseph.github.io/blog/post/the-hidden-costs-of-convenience/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://i.pinimg.com/1200x/f6/3a/7e/f63a7e41e43c1cb581b5cd1e2d7a45fa.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;The Hidden Costs Of Convenience&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Algorithmic feeds are convenient, but they&apos;re also a string. It matters who controls that string and what they&apos;re doing with it.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://romiojoseph.github.io/blog/post/the-hidden-costs-of-convenience/&quot;&gt;Read more on the blog...&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 02 Feb 2026 00:30:00 GMT</pubDate></item><item><title>You Are Absolutely Right!</title><link>https://romiojoseph.github.io/blog/post/you-are-absolutely-right/</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://romiojoseph.github.io/blog/post/you-are-absolutely-right/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://i.pinimg.com/1200x/98/53/c1/9853c1a95cb71b25625a8097083ee746.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;You Are Absolutely Right!&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;This is written from a vibe coder’s perspective. If you&apos;re already an experienced developer, this blog probably won’t offer anything new.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://romiojoseph.github.io/blog/post/you-are-absolutely-right/&quot;&gt;Read more on the blog...&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 17 Nov 2025 00:30:00 GMT</pubDate></item><item><title>Writing Tools</title><link>https://romiojoseph.github.io/blog/post/writing-tools/</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://romiojoseph.github.io/blog/post/writing-tools/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://romiojoseph.github.io/assets/cover-images/featured/notes.avif&quot; alt=&quot;Writing Tools&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;The fact that you can just build simple things with LLMs is a nice to have feature for the future. I hope things keep getting better over time.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://romiojoseph.github.io/blog/post/writing-tools/&quot;&gt;Read more on the blog...&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 30 Apr 2025 00:30:00 GMT</pubDate></item><item><title>Vibe Coding</title><link>https://romiojoseph.github.io/blog/post/vibe-coding/</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://romiojoseph.github.io/blog/post/vibe-coding/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!EB6C!,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fbe5fb813-53a0-4504-900a-d76a84f6ebf0_1000x453.png&quot; alt=&quot;Vibe Coding&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Write longer posts, experience Bluesky in any layout imaginable, integrate Bluesky comments into your site, and more.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://romiojoseph.github.io/blog/post/vibe-coding/&quot;&gt;Read more on the blog...&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 21 Apr 2025 00:30:00 GMT</pubDate></item><item><title>Bluesky Comments Widget: Add replies to your site</title><link>https://romiojoseph.github.io/blog/post/bluesky-comments-widget/</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://romiojoseph.github.io/blog/post/bluesky-comments-widget/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://raw.githubusercontent.com/romiojoseph/bluesky/refs/heads/main/bluesky-comments-widget/assets/social-image.png&quot; alt=&quot;Bluesky Comments Widget: Add replies to your site&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Share your page link on Bluesky, then use this widget to show replies as comments on your site. No login or authentication needed.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://romiojoseph.github.io/blog/post/bluesky-comments-widget/&quot;&gt;Read more on the blog...&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 14 Apr 2025 00:30:00 GMT</pubDate></item><item><title>New Horizons</title><link>https://romiojoseph.github.io/blog/post/new-horizons-real-time-news-via-bluesky/</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://romiojoseph.github.io/blog/post/new-horizons-real-time-news-via-bluesky/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://romiojoseph.github.io/new-horizons/social-image.png&quot; alt=&quot;New Horizons&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Aggregates real-time news from Bluesky media profiles, tech companies, organizations, institutions, and journalists, along with threads from Hacker News.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://romiojoseph.github.io/blog/post/new-horizons-real-time-news-via-bluesky/&quot;&gt;Read more on the blog...&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 04 Feb 2025 00:30:00 GMT</pubDate></item><item><title>Everything I Built Around Movies</title>