c885d.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;10,000 Hours&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Even projects that seem to go nowhere contribute to progress through exploration. It&apos;s about messing around and seeing what happens.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://romiojoseph.github.io/blog/post/ai-assisted-learning-journey-10000-hours-snowball-effect/&quot;&gt;Read more on the blog...&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 02 Oct 2024 00:30:00 GMT</pubDate></item><item><title>Godfather</title><link>https://romiojoseph.github.io/blog/post/the-godfather-by-francis-ford-coppola/</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://romiojoseph.github.io/blog/post/the-godfather-by-francis-ford-coppola/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!AjDA!,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F5b8d171c-01ae-4bd8-a4c8-b197a9af8595_1920x1080.png&quot; alt=&quot;Michael and Vito Corleone discuss potential threats and how Vito never wanted Michael in this position in the first installment of The Godfather series.&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;A movie trilogy you can&apos;t refuse to watch countless times.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://romiojoseph.github.io/blog/post/the-godfather-by-francis-ford-coppola/&quot;&gt;Read more on the blog...&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 26 Aug 2024 13:16:00 GMT</pubDate></item><item><title>Free Alternatives</title><link>https://romiojoseph.github.io/blog/post/free-alternatives-decentralize-tech-open-source/</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://romiojoseph.github.io/blog/post/free-alternatives-decentralize-tech-open-source/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!Clvh!,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F7470d0c7-6e8a-4013-b6c4-23b7d8d44e41_1360x768.jpeg&quot; alt=&quot;Free Alternatives&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;