tps://romiojoseph.github.io/blog/post/repurpose-old-laptop-with-ubuntu-or-chromeosflex/&quot;&gt;Read more on the blog...&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 09 May 2024 00:30:00 GMT</pubDate></item><item><title>Software Data Ownership and Portability</title><link>https://romiojoseph.github.io/blog/post/open-design-tools-data-ownership-portability/</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://romiojoseph.github.io/blog/post/open-design-tools-data-ownership-portability/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!u7pI!,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F05dc3e8a-7970-4cd4-8a6b-b341121e36ab_1360x768.jpeg&quot; alt=&quot;Software Data Ownership and Portability&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Open file formats, an interoperable ecosystem, and self-hosting options ensure we have the power to manage our digital assets on our own terms.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://romiojoseph.github.io/blog/post/open-design-tools-data-ownership-portability/&quot;&gt;Read more on the blog...&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Sat, 23 Mar 2024 00:30:00 GMT</pubDate></item><item><title>The Pale Blue Dot</title><link>https://romiojoseph.github.io/blog/post/the-pale-blue-dot/</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://romiojoseph.github.io/blog/post/the-pale-blue-dot/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://cdn.bsky.app/img/feed_fullsize/plain/did:plc:xglrcj6gmrpktysohindaqhj/bafkreihs47fnbj5kiexi7766dv7bptn5jf4oidlp2fbwsb2jjmbpk63l5a&quot; alt=&quot;PIA23645: Pale Blue Dot Revisited | Image Credit: NASA/JPL-Caltech&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Thinking about our place in the universe.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://romiojoseph.github.io/blog/post/the-pale-blue-dot/&quot;&gt;Read more on the blog...&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 09 Feb 2024 00:30:00 GMT</pubDate></item><item><title>Writing Is A Learning</title><link>https://romiojoseph.github.io/blog/post/writing-is-a-learning/</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://romiojoseph.github.io/blog/post/writing-is-a-learning/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1654484521164-92bf7605cac0?crop=entropy&amp;cs=tinysrgb&amp;fit=max&amp;fm=jpg&amp;ixid=M3wzMDAzMzh8MHwxfHNlYXJjaHwyNDd8fG1lY2hhbmljYWwlMjBrZXlib2FyZHxlbnwwfHx8fDE3MDE5MzkyNjN8MA&amp;ixlib=rb-4.0.3&amp;q=80&amp;w=1080&quot; alt=&quot;Photo by Rama Laksono on Unsplash&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;What to write, and what not to write depends on us. In this post, I&apos;m analyzing why I wanted to be an independent writer and not just a designer.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://romiojoseph.github.io/blog/post/writing-is-a-learning/&quot;&gt;Read more on the blog...&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 Dec 2023 00:30:00 GMT</pubDate></item><item><title>Movies, Documentaries, Shows, Specials and Music</title><link>https://romiojoseph.github.io/blog/post/movies-documentaries-shows-specials-and-music/</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://romiojoseph.github.io/blog/post/movies-documentaries-shows-specials-and-music/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!fk3F!,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fbucketeer-e05bbc84-baa3-437e-9518-adb32be77984.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F51fb0ebb-939c-4d98-9ff0-be38359fc4c7_1526x828.png&quot; alt=&quot;Movies, Documentaries, Shows, Specials and Music&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;I never made a serious effort to log everything. Just a few, whenever I felt the need to get something out. You can find those links here.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://romiojoseph.github.io/blog/post/movies-documentaries-shows-specials-and-music/&quot;&gt;Read more on the blog...&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Sun, 25 Sep 2022 00:30:00 GMT</pubDate></item><item><title>The Curious Case of Losing Someone From Our Life</title><link>https://romiojoseph.github.io/blog/post/the-curious-case-of-losing-someone-from-our-life/</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://romiojoseph.github.io/blog/post/the-curious-case-of-losing-someone-from-our-life/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1542159919831-40fb0656b45a?crop=entropy&amp;cs=tinysrgb&amp;fit=max&amp;fm=jpg&amp;ixid=MnwzMDAzMzh8MHwxfHNlYXJjaHwxMnx8c3Vuc2V0fGVufDB8fHx8MTY1NzIyNTE0OA&amp;ixlib=rb-1.2.1&amp;q=80&amp;w=1080&quot; alt=&quot;Photo by David Mullins on Unsplash&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Death. It’s inevitable. Today or tomorrow, that’s all we know.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://romiojoseph.github.io/blog/post/the-curious-case-of-losing-someone-from-our-life/&quot;&gt;Read more on the blog...&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 08 Jul 2022 00:30:00 GMT</pubDate></item><item><title>Murphy&apos;s Law</title><link>https://romiojoseph.github.io/blog/post/why-murphys-law/</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://romiojoseph.github.io/blog/post/why-murphys-law/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!AngF!,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fbucketeer-e05bbc84-baa3-437e-9518-adb32be77984.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F4dfddbb7-3c8a-426b-ba28-664ea8c5f377_2560x1440.png&quot; alt=&quot;Murphy&apos;s Law - Whatever can happen, will happen.&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Whatever can happen, will happen.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://romiojoseph.github.io/blog/post/why-murphys-law/&quot;&gt;Read more on the blog...&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Sat, 28 Mar 2020 00:30:00 GMT</pubDate></item><item><title>From Archives</title><link>https://romiojoseph.github.io/blog/post/from-archives/</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://romiojoseph.github.io/blog/post/from-archives/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!D77r!,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_pr